## Phase 4: Proactive Context Enrichment

### [NEW] [src/enrichment.js](file:///c:/Users/omara/ai-assistant/src/enrichment.js)

When the user asks for something, run a quick parallel "enrichment" step:
- Flight search → also fetch destination weather
- Email draft → verify recipient exists in contacts
- Meeting scheduling → check calendar conflicts
- File operations → check disk space

**Implementation:** A simple map of task patterns → enrichment functions. Runs in parallel with the main action. Results are injected into the conversation as additional context.

**This is what creates the "wow I didn't even think about that" moments.**

